create new app on heroku
download and install heroku CLI
npm install -g heroku
heroku --version
heroku login

go to project folder

git init
heroku git:remote -a <app name in heroku->springboot-first-heroku-app>
git add .
git commit -am "any msg here"
git push heroku master

for configuring database in heroku

create new app
go to resources
then add-ons
search heroku postgres
submit form 
click on the app name
settings
view credentials
congfigure heroku postgres credentials in projects application.properties file
then deploy